{"tid":1996014,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"學生設計手足：自力更生，設計咗啲杯希望大家支持","createTime":"2020-04-30T16:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T18:48:06.000Z","uid":291093,"like":40,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1a5cff25068424ee802c884a4b6963c5d25af499","tid":1996014,"uid":291093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:29:49.000Z","msg":"抗爭半年，面對住高昂嘅<strong>生活費、學費、器材費</strong>，卻換來屋企人嘅冷嘲熱諷<br />\n<br />\n坦白講，抗爭要用錢、要食飯，啲錢唔會喺個天度跌落嚟。雖然有坊間唔少資助/贊助手足生活嘅計劃，但我有手有腳，唔甘心攤大手板問人拎錢。我哋相信，可以慿自己的雙手、知識、技能去改變現況。<br />\n<br />\n同埋長遠嚟講想裝備下自己，唔通一世都靠嗰啲贊助計劃？我哋知道，有更多更多手足比我們更有需要用到那筆費用。<br />\n<br />\n作為設計學生，我哋決定設計一啲抗爭日用品，嘗試日常化抗爭，讓人無時無刻謹記勿忘初衷。<br />\n<br />\n你可能覺得噁心又醜樣，但我哋設計嘅心血、心思係出面冇一度買到，希望可以支持我哋。<br />\n<br />\n連結：<a href=\"https://igg.me/at/swhkcup/x#/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Figg.me%2Fat%2Fswhkcup%2Fx%23%2F&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=8751f075\" target=\"_blank\">https://igg.me/at/swhkcup/x#/</a><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hker.art\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhker.art&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=20704aab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hker.art</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RRhtsLb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRRhtsLb.png&h=50236305&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e51d14760afbd1b974f35ee05fce855affce251a","tid":1996014,"uid":291093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:31:35.000Z","msg":"P牌仔冇得推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c29cadec152a2ca4b0e717ac510c029095087a","tid":1996014,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:33:50.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n設計喺香港唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2fda24374763155e911ff29adb2e860bed3e7d","tid":1996014,"uid":298126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多啲設計呢啲野等我地大力懲罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e364f7857361bcb86ac4f6a10cb6efbe599b5a","tid":1996014,"uid":291093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:39:47.000Z","msg":"今次畫作係由依位手足設計，大家記住follow：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/wlonghahaha99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwlonghahaha99&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=f8016480\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/wlonghahaha99</a>"},{"pid":"45bded6f6f05c643f7a9b689cb7715a06159c4f4","tid":1996014,"uid":291093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22c29cadec152a2ca4b0e717ac510c029095087a","tid":1996014,"uid":146717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:33:50.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n設計喺香港唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:41:33.000Z","msg":"THX CHING 香港玩設計，一係就好掂，一係就乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa44028a32324e84eb9b5022eaaa1862b520630","tid":1996014,"uid":291093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d2fda24374763155e911ff29adb2e860bed3e7d","tid":1996014,"uid":298126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多啲設計呢啲野等我地大力懲罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:42:14.000Z","msg":"Thx for support."},{"pid":"8089ce8a96a45b2534049bd880c032ec46ccc87b","tid":1996014,"uid":201721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"